Package timeseries.models

Statistical models for time series data.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Forecast
    A forecast produced by a time series Model.
    Model
    A time series model.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MeanForecast
    A mean model forecast.
    MeanModel
    A time series model that assumes no trend or seasonal factors are present, and that puts as much weight on early values of the series as it does on recent values.
    RandomWalk
    A model for a random walk process.
    RandomWalkForecast
    A forecast from a random walk model.
